game_description: KUBIKOS set is a set of low poly, cartoony, building blocks. Game contains Egypt world, Platformer world, dungeon, published to date (100+ objects) and will be added to overtime. Features: *Add more than 1000+ object with out losing fps *Autosave. Your progress never be erased *You can build dungeon, castle *Build with out limit. *One of the best simulation games: begin constructing your dream world *Enjoy the visual and sound effects. *Build your own construction
